body.name: NCVI Baby Formula Dispenser On The Go, Formula Container to Go, Formula Holder for Travel, Outdoor Picnic with Baby Infant, Portable Container for Milk Powder, Snacks, Candy, Fruits (Green)
deliveryMessages: FREE delivery Saturday, February 24 on orders shipped by Amazon over $35
features: MILK POWDER DISPENSER: The NCVI baby formula container is made of high food-grade PP plastic that is BPA-free, environmentally friendly, suitable for moist- heat and freezer safe as well. This milk dispenser for baby formula has two cute horns that is made from TPE soft material, which is round, soft and safe.

KEEPS THE FOOD FRESH AND SAFE: This baby milk powder formula dispenser has a buckle design and silicone sealing ring inner lid ensuring food is fresh and preventing formula from getting wet and from any damage. The lovely horn on the top of travel formula dispenser keeps it stable while adding it. It is easy to clean and dry.

Multiple Compartments: A milk powder dispenser is a great way to store your formula. It has multiple compartments so you can keep the spoon separate from the formula. This keeps out of dirt and dust. The leveller design helps you scoop out each spoonful of formula precisely without wasting.

WIDELY APPLICABLE: The formula container is used to store 230g of powdered milk. It can hold about 30 scoops (1 scoop = 5.0g). This dispenser is easy to use, just be ready to feed, add the powder into the feeding bottle of pre-boiled water, shake it and feed your baby. The container also works as a fruit storage container, snack cup for cookies and other similar items.

EASY TRAVELER BOX: It is transparent, allows you to see the contents clearly. The box has a scale which makes it easy to determine how much milk powder is left inside. This milk powder dispenser is of the ideal size for portability. It fits in bags and hands and comes in handy while travelling and visiting friends, or relatives with babies. It even makes on-the-go feeding easier.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 8, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A must have!
reviews.reviewText: The NCVI Baby Formula Dispenser has been a game-changer for my on-the-go parenting needs. Its compact design and smart dispensing feature make it an essential travel companion. I no longer worry about messy spills or formula wastage when preparing bottles on the move. This dispenser’s versatility extends beyond formula, as it’s perfect for storing snacks and nuts as my child’s dietary needs evolve. The quality build and the included scoop with a leveller ensure precise measurements every time. Plus, the charming purple color not only adds a cute touch but also makes it easy to spot in my bag. It’s a must-have for parents looking for a reliable and convenient solution to feeding their little ones while out and about.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 6, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars cute and works well
reviews.reviewText: Its very easy to open and close, even one handed. The bottom doesn't slip around easily when you're scooping stuff from it. I use it for formula currently, and it hasn't leaked at all. it's a great size to fit a pretty good amount into without having to worry about running out, and also fits well in a diaper bag to carry around without taking up too much room for diapers and such. The spoon that comes eith it is half the size of the scoops provided with most formulas is the only downside, as you have to remember to use the right amount if formula.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 8, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Exactly what I needed!
reviews.reviewText: I love this little container!! It’s perfect for an overnight stay or day trip somewhere. It holds 30 scoops of formula perfectly, for us that’s 2 full days worth of bottles. The only thing that I was disappointed with is the scoop it comes with. It’s cute! But it’s not an accurate scoop for formula. The scoop from the formula bin fits laying sideways on the top so it’s not a big deal! Other than that, this is great!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 11, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars So cute, so efficient
reviews.reviewText: I love this thing! It’s cute, and easy to be cleaned. It holds a tremendous amount of formula. The scoop it comes with is 1/2 scoop of the scoop that comes with similac formula. I don’t mind it because it allows me to make odd ounce bottles. I’m so happy with my purchase!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 28, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I was expecting it to be bigger than what it is, but I am glad it wasn’t bigger…this one fits perfect into a diaper bag. The scoop that comes with it was way too small for the amount of formula needed to use so I switched it myself. No powder escapes due to it having a great seal when latched on properly. Great for traveling & packing into small bags.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 9, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I purchased this formula dispenser for a short road trip. I have used several other variations of formula dispensers and this has to be my favorite. My kiddos formula intake ranges and having a pre measured option just wasn’t going to work. This dispenser is easy to fill and it would usually last a full day before needing to be refilled. The small measuring spoon is too small and I ended up reusing one of the spoons that comes with his formula. I just didn’t want to deal with the whole conversions of small spoon to big spoon. I love love love that it doesn’t take much space, at all! The product is durable, easy to use, secure (has never opened or spilled on me), and purchased for a great price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 11, 2024
reviews.reviewText: While not completely something you must have as essential, this little container is extremely and utterly cute also eye catching. Stores your formula powder well and tidy. I have a Doona Essentials bag and it fits right in, no problem. Algo, it is great to carry on your diaper caddy when cooking a quick bottle. People love it when I pulled it out on restaurants and get why the cow! Super adorable.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 1, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I love this formula container. It is perfect size for my diaper bag, plus it’s super cute! The scoop however, is smaller than the formula can scoop, so I just included the one from my can. To me, it’s no big deal, but that would be the only flaw. You can still use the scoop that comes with it if you did not want to include your own. It’s just one scoop to one ounce water. But again, it’s super cute…. Seals tightly…. Very convenient for on the go…. Overall, I would definitely recommend this product!
